ming and reserved; Pasini, a cocky womanizer; Mitis, gruff and sagacious. The three have been best friends for as long as they can remember, but Fred's arrival puts their longstanding bond to the test. As each of the guys secretly desires Fred for himself, she yearns to be accepted into the group and be considered 'one of them', but is asked to sacrifice more and more in order to belong.","poster_path":"/6Oha80OEhmtnDwlRYrdvLXP0mmo.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"it","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.0536,"release_date":"2026-04-09","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.3,"vote_count":13}]},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":5777430,"known_for_department":"Camera","name":"Laura Guerra Samaniego","original_name":"Laura Guerra Samaniego","popularity":0.0,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"id":1569911,"title":"Confession","original_title":"Spowiedź","overview":"The film “Confession” is an experimental form that deals with the topic of queerness, belonging, identity, religion, and love.","poster_path":null,"media_type":"movie","original_language":"en","genre_ids":[],"popularity":0.0357,"release_date":"2025-08-26","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":0.0,"vote_count":0}]}],"total_pages":1,"total_results":2}